  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving Health Service Infrastructure in Kono district</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Contribute  to support the government recovery plan to restore health services and
plan towards building a robust, resilience healthcare system</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rehabilitation of three-four PHUs in Kono and Kailahun Districts
completion of the PHU construction and provide it with necessary equipment and furnishings including delivery beds and kits, mattresses, a blood pressure machine and drug storage facilities Provision of reliable electricity to the supported
PHUs via solar equipment.
rehabilitation of wells serving the PHUs and rehabilitation of toilets, as well as provision of sanitary methods for dumping waste.
Capacity building and support to strengthen DHMT monitoring and supervision of PHUs
Building community ownership of the PHUs to ensure sustainability</narrative>
  </description>
